column5: Hello all I'm up in Owen Sound right now camping and I was just wondering if anyone would know we're I could get worm and live bait here...thanks in advance
watsons, hes on 125, 14th st west, doubt hes got minnows this time of year though
Looked like Watson's Tackle was rebuilding when I was up there a while ago. Fire maybe?
Thanks went there today and got worms and roe... Any decent spots to fish here we were at the dock by a big steel ship but no luck
